rows.label: qst002302_msg0002
rows.name:
23 guards in Cathedral at night?
Thanks much for valuable info.

rows.label: qst002302_msg0003
rows.name:
My dear Moruru, you wouldn't happen
to be plotting anything unsavory again,
now, would you?

rows.label: qst002302_msg0004
rows.name:
Meh-meh?!
Wh-why Moruru would plot things?

rows.label: qst002302_msg0005
rows.name:
Moruru just here to listen to very
inspiring talks about glorious teachings
of Marveni-sama!

rows.label: qst002302_msg0006
rows.name: Very well. I will trust you in this...

rows.label: qst002302_msg0007
rows.name:
By the by, perhaps you could ask these
fine people to deliver the item we were
discussing to Maurcio?

rows.label: qst002302_msg0009
rows.name:
Your path forward will not reveal itself
until you take action, young one.

rows.label: qst002302_msg0011
rows.name:
Could friends do one more little
favor for Moruru?

rows.label: qst002302_msg0012
rows.name:
Moruru want friends to deliver
Platinum Music Box to Maurcio
at Goth Isut Port.

rows.label: qst002302_msg0014
rows.name:
Young Moruru, your future will surely
be blessed by God.
